## 5. GREG.CS PUBLIC API FACADE

The static `greg` class provides lazy-initialized access to all framework modules:

```csharp
// Economy
greg.Economy.GetBalance(playerId);
greg.Economy.AddMoney(playerId, amount);
greg.Economy.RemoveMoney(playerId, amount);
greg.Economy.SetBalance(playerId, amount);

// Player
greg.Player.GetCurrent();
greg.Player.GetLevel();
greg.Player.GetInventory();
greg.Player.UpdateInventory(itemId, quantity);

// Server
greg.Server.GetAll();
greg.Server.GetById(serverId);
greg.Server.Create(config);
greg.Server.Destroy(serverId);

// Rack
greg.Facility.GetRacks();
greg.Facility.GetRackById(rackId);
greg.Facility.PlaceRack(position, type);
greg.Facility.RemoveRack(rackId);

// Network
greg.Network.SendMessage(recipientId, messageType, payload);
greg.Network.Broadcast(messageType, payload);
greg.Network.GetConnections();

// Automation
greg.Automation.Queue(task);
greg.Automation.GetQueuedTasks();
greg.Automation.CancelTask(taskId);

// UI
greg.UI.ShowNotification(title, message);
greg.UI.ShowDialog(title, message, buttons);
greg.UI.HideDialog(dialogId);
greg.UI.GetActiveMenu();

// Save
greg.Save.Persist(key, value);
greg.Save.Load(key);
greg.Save.Delete(key);
greg.Save.Flush();

// NPC
greg.Npc.GetAllCustomers();
greg.Npc.GetAllEmployees();
greg.Npc.GetById(npcId);

// Performance
greg.Performance.SetFrameBudget(milliseconds);
greg.Performance.GetMetrics();
greg.Performance.GCCollect();

// Time
greg.Time.GetGameTime();
greg.Time.GetServerTime();
greg.Time.SetTimeScale(scale);
```

All module properties are lazy-initialized on first access.

