## 15. UI / ASSETS (UNITY 6000.4+)

### FORBIDDEN: IMGUI / OnGUI
```csharp
// WRONG ❌ — Will crash instantly
void OnGUI()
{
    if (GUILayout.Button("Click me"))
    {
        // ...
    }
}
```

### REQUIRED: UI Toolkit
```csharp
public override void OnUpdate()
{
    if (!_uiCreated)
    {
        CreateUI();
        _uiCreated = true;
    }
}

private void CreateUI()
{
    var root = new VisualElement();
    root.style.width = Length.Percent(100);
    root.style.height = Length.Percent(100);

    var button = new Button(() => OnButtonClicked());
    button.text = "Click Me";
    root.Add(button);

    // Attach to screen
    var panel = UIDocument.GetComponent<UIDocument>();
    panel.rootVisualElement = root;
}

private void OnButtonClicked()
{
    MelonLogger.Msg("Button clicked!");
}
```

### Asset Loading Priority
```csharp
// 1. AssetBundle (preferred for mods)
var bundle = AssetBundle.LoadFromFile("path/to/bundle.ab");
var prefab = bundle.LoadAsset<GameObject>("MyPrefab");

// 2. Addressables
var handle = Addressables.LoadAssetAsync<GameObject>("my_key");
var obj = handle.Result;

// 3. Resources.Load (fallback)
var obj = Resources.Load<GameObject>("Prefabs/MyPrefab");
```

### NO YAML Direct Edits
```csharp
// WRONG ❌
File.WriteAllText("Assets/Scenes/MyScene.unity", modifiedYaml);

// RIGHT ✅
GameObject scene = Instantiate(Resources.Load<GameObject>("Scenes/MyScene"));
// Modify at runtime
```

